                  "revisionId": 2768438,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Grants 75% electricity damage and 75% electricity status damage."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Conductive Sphere",
                  "pageId": 1595877,
                  "revisionId": 2768438,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Electricity damage bonus is additive with electricity damage sources, such as Stormbringer . However, unlike modded electricity damage, this bonus is not counted in the \"electricity damage bonuses\" portion of the status damage calculation (bug), and therefore does not add any damage to electricity statuses. See Electricity Damage for the status damage formula."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Conductive Sphere",
                  "pageId": 1595877,
                  "revisionId": 2768438,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Electricity status damage bonus stacks additively with status damage sources, such as Rifle Elementalist . The bonus only applies to electricity procs, but works on both the guaranteed electric procs from this augment and natural electric procs from the weapon."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Conductive Sphere",
                  "pageId": 1595877,
                  "revisionId": 2768438,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "This behavior is after the U38.6 patch, which was supposed to fix the status damage calculation."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Conductive Sphere",
                  "pageId": 1595877,
                  "revisionId": 2768438,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Shooting through multiple arcspheres will grant additional guaranteed electric procs and electricity damage, but will not grant additional electricity status damage."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Conductive Sphere",
                  "pageId": 1595877,
                  "revisionId": 2768438,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Projectiles only need to pass through the Arcsphere 's electric field in order to gain the bonus, not the arcsphere object itself."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Conductive Sphere",
                  "pageId": 1595877,
                  "revisionId": 2768438,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Standing within the electric field will trigger the bonus on all shots fired."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Conductive Sphere",
                  "pageId": 1595877,
                  "revisionId": 2768438,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Non-projectile (hitscan, beam, etc) weapons can trigger the effect as well, whether by shooting through the sphere or standing within it."
                }
              },
